    "Management": {
      "text": "Avoid immobilization\nPhysical therapy\nAnalgesia\nNSAIDs\n,\nopioids\nOral\nsteroids\nProvide significant short-term benefit in terms of relieving pain and improving ROM\nIntra-articular steroids (20-40mg triamcinolone)\nBenefits last a few months, possibly up to 6 months\n[1]\nJoint distention\nIntra-articular distention with 25-40mL of saline + anesthetic is as effective as IA steroids\n[2]",
